					<msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597" rend="visible">
						<summary>The Pentateuch with Rashi's commentary and Targum Onḳelos, Hafṭarot with David Kimḥi's commentary and  Five Scrolls with various commentaries.</summary>
						<textLang mainLang="he" otherLangs="tmr-Hebr">Hebrew, Aramaic</textLang>
