							<title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Torah, hafṭarot u-megilot</title>
							<title xml:lang="he">תורה, הפטרות ומגילות</title>
							<decoNote type="other">
								<locus n="1r"/> 	1 historiated initial-word panel, in colours and gold.</decoNote>
							<decoNote type="initial">
								<locus n="76v, 142v, 191r, 254v"/>4 decorated initial-word panels inhabited by birds, in colours and gold.</decoNote>
							<decoNote type="initial">
